@page "/Terms"

<MarketingHero Title="Terms of"
               Highlight="service"
               Subtitle="The agreement you accept when you book freight or apply to drive." />

<div class="Card">
    <h2 class="CardTitle">Service</h2>
    <p>Wolfs Trucking Co. provides freight transportation, marketplace listings, and driver placement services. Booking a shipment or accepting a job through this platform constitutes acceptance of these terms.</p>
    <h2 class="CardTitle" style="margin-top:18px">Liability</h2>
    <p>Cargo insurance up to $100,000 per shipment. Higher value shipments require declared-value rider. Acts of God excluded.</p>
    <h2 class="CardTitle" style="margin-top:18px">Disputes</h2>
    <p>California law governs. Arbitration in Los Angeles County for claims under $25,000. Jury waiver applies.</p>
</div>
